OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,FITV News reporter Rachel Hepworth
OL,7,Ftalks to two of Orchard's victims and
OL,8,Finvestigating officer PC Steve Cann
OL,9,Ffrom Hampshire Police.
OL,11,F"It was a total betrayal. I felt sorry
OL,12,Ffor him, tried to include him, and
OL,13,Fthis is how he treated me. It's
OL,14,Fdisgusting."
OL,16,FGeorgia Horton finds it hard to
OL,17,Fbelieve that a man she knew, and
OL,18,Ftrusted, could violate her privacy in
OL,19,Fsuch a way.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
