OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,FShe'd never been close to Ethan
OL,7,FOrchard, but ten years ago she was at
OL,8,Fcollege in Hampshire with him.
OL,10,FHe was a bit of a loner, so she
OL,11,Freached out, they struck up a
OL,12,Ffriendship, and had remained in touch,
OL,13,Fmostly on-line, ever since.
OL,15,FThat was until she discovered he'd
OL,16,Fdownloaded innocent images of her from
OL,17,Fsocial media, manipulated them using
OL,18,FAI to make them pornographic, and
OL,19,Fasked other men to share their violent
OL,20,Fand sexual fantasies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
