FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,FShe was one of three women, all known
OL,7,Fto each other, who'd been targeted.
OL,9,F"He would make them choose between us,
OL,10,For say what they wanted do to us, "
OL,11,Fsays Georgia,
OL,13,F"One of the posts was 'what would you
OL,14,Fdo if you had five minutes alone with
OL,15,Fher?' And it got so much worse from
OL,16,Fthere.
OL,18,FThe worst one I probably had was,
OL,19,F'Would you save her? Would you rape
OL,20,Fher, or would you sell her?'
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
