OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,FWATCH : The moment Orchard is
OL,7,Fconfronted with the evidence in police
OL,8,Finterview.
OL,10,FAnother of his victims, who wants to
OL,11,Fremain anonymous - we'll call her
OL,12,FSarah - can no longer look at her
OL,13,Fwedding photos, which Orchard
OL,14,Fdigitally altered and shared on the
OL,15,Fillegal website.
OL,17,F"I don't know why he chose those
OL,18,Fphotos," she says. "Using someone's
OL,19,Fmost treasured day, taking something
OL,20,Fyou can't replace and destroying it.
OL,21,FIt's just heartbreaking.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
