PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,F"It's affected my husband, my family.
OL,7,FI can never look at them in the same
OL,8,Fway."
OL,10,FThrough enquiries, Hampshire police
OL,11,Fwere able to identify Orchard as the
OL,12,Fperson responsible for uploading the
OL,13,Fimages ` The 30-year-old, of Highland
OL,14,FRoad in Southsea, was known to Sarah
OL,15,Fand even made her aware of the images
OL,16,Fbeing shared, but did not disclose to
OL,17,Fher that he was the person responsible.
OL,19,FIn addition, Orchard encouraged others
OL,20,Fonline to harass Sarah, disclosing her
OL,21,Faddress and contact details.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
