PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,F"I was scared for myself and my
OL,7,Ffamily, " says Sarah. "I moved houses,
OL,8,FI changed jobs. I didn't know who was
OL,9,Flooking at my photos. I didn't know
OL,10,Fwho was seeing my information."
OL,12,FOrchard was arrested and later charged
OL,13,Fwith three counts of sharing a
OL,14,Fphotograph of a person in an intimate
OL,15,Fstate for the purpose of sexual
OL,16,Fgratification, and one count of
OL,17,Fencouraging the commission of an
OL,18,Feither way offence and believing it
OL,19,Fwill be committed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
