PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to the offences on
OL,7,F11 May this year, and was jailed for
OL,8,Fthree years and four months on Friday
OL,9,F10 July. He was also made subject to a
OL,10,F10 year Sexual Harm Prevention Order,
OL,11,Fand was given an indefinite
OL,12,Frestraining order.
OL,14,F"It's got real world consequences, and
OL,15,Fthat's what I don't think people
OL,16,Frealise when they're doing this with
OL,17,FAI" said investigating office PC Steve
OL,18,FCann. "It isn't just a bit of harmless
OL,19,Ffun- there are real world
OL,20,Fconsequences."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
