CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,FThe investigation also led to the
OL,7,Fdiscovery and closure of a website
OL,8,Fwhere his images were uploaded.
OL,10,FPC Cann contacted the FBI, aware that
OL,11,Fthe site domain had been seized by the
OL,12,FFlorida Department of Law Enforcement
OL,13,F(FDLE).
OL,15,FIt was being used to advertise
OL,16,Findecent images of children and make
OL,17,Fcontact with buyers who wanted to buy
OL,18,Fchild abuse material.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
