PN,38109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,FThe FDLE's cyber team then set about
OL,7,Fseizing the website domain and
OL,8,Fremoving the website, and were able to
OL,9,Fseize 1.1million indecent images of
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FAuthorities were also able to identify
OL,13,Fmore than 50 victims of child sex
OL,14,Fabuse spanning the United States,
OL,15,FCanada, Australia and the UK.
OL,17,FLegal proceedings are now underway
OL,18,Fagainst a number of individuals
OL,19,Fworldwide.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
