FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,FPC Cann is delighted to have helped;
OL,7,F"It's good knowing what's happened.
OL,8,FRemoving over a million images of
OL,9,Fchildren off the internet, and every
OL,10,Fsingle one of them is a victim.
OL,12,F"This all came about because one lady
OL,13,Fhad the courage to come to the police
OL,14,Fand go, 'no, this isn't right.' "
OL,16,FThe force wants to highlight that on-
OL,17,Fline abuse IS taken seriously and will
OL,18,Fbe investigated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,F"If you're doing it, just stop it. In
OL,7,Fthe end, these photos will be there
OL,8,Fforever.
OL,10,F"If you get discovered doing that,
OL,11,Fthat's your life destroyed. That's
OL,12,Fyour victim's life is destroyed.
OL,14,F"It's just not worth it for the small
OL,15,Fsense of satisfaction you might get. "
OL,17,FSarah and Georgia are moving on with
OL,18,Ftheir lives, but are urging others to
OL,19,Fbe vigilant about the images they
OL,20,Fshare on-line.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
