PN,38112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784915311
OL,3,CFantasist who faked obscene images of
OL,4,Cbride jailed
OL,6,F"It's so dangerous," says Georgia.
OL,7,F"It's so easy nowadays for people, for
OL,8,Fpredators to pick up a picture online.
OL,10,F"Most of my friends post pictures of
OL,11,Ftheir kids on social media. And it
OL,12,Ftakes one photo to be put through AI
OL,13,Fand it's limitless, the damage that
OL,14,Fcan be done."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
